e%20in%20global%20markets%20and%20global%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banking%2C%20this%20person%20added.%20The%20cuts%20were%20first%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Fbank-america-eliminates-some-investment-banking-roles-including-new-york-2025-03-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReuters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESid%20Khosla%2C%20a%20financial%20services%20executive%20at%20EY%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20firm's%20banking%20and%20capital%20markets%20leader%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20such%20layoffs%20are%20part%20of%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bthe%20efficiency%20conversation%26quot%3B%20among%20companies%20seeking%20to%20please%20shareholders%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trend%20that%20started%20before%20Trump%20took%20office.%20The%20topic%20has%20come%20up%20increasingly%20in%20talks%20with%20clients%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20past%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20Khosla%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20the%20top%20two%20or%20three%20conversations.%20Some%20institutions%20may%20think%20it's%20a%20No.%201%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20corporate%20dealmaking%20picks%20back%20up%20depends%20on%20how%20long%20the%20turmoil%20lasts%2C%20bankers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20any%20reasonable%20outlook%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20little%20clouded%20here%20for%20a%20while%20because%20there's%20no%20certainty%20that%20the%20conversations%20around%20tariffs%20and%20the%20concerns%20around%20the%20US%20economy%20or%20around%20interest%20rates%20are%20going%20to%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Stowe%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20certainty%20that%20the%20current%20level%20of%20volatility%20will%20dissipate%20in%20the%20near%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReed%20Alexander%20is%20a%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20Wall%20Street%20and%20financial%20services.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20v