20OK%20not%20to%20be%20OK%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20Illinois%20made%20a%20bold%20move.%20The%20state%20passed%20a%20law%20allowing%20kindergarten%20to%20high%20school%20students%20to%20take%20up%20to%20five%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foregon-students-mental-health-days-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexcused%20mental%20health%20days%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-gentle-parenting-and-how-to-follow-it-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20mom%20of%20four%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20two%20teenagers%2C%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20this%20option.%20In%20my%20family%2C%20we%20have%20multiple%20diagnoses%2C%20including%20anxiety%20disorders%2C%20that%20make%20mental%20health%20days%20not%20only%20appreciated%20but%20essential.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22849b18b5-82c1-4bee-ac55-86a59c655af8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20a%20teen%20can%20be%20hard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdolescence%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-teens-is-a-balance-too-close-or-too-far-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecan%20be%20tumultuous%20for%20teens%2C%20parents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20coaches.%20It's%20not%20surprising%20that%20some%20teens%20wind%20up%20diagnosed%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20common%20mental%20health%20disorders%20during%20their%20middle%20and%20high%20school%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%2015%25%20of%20tweens%20and%20teens%20have%20a%20mental%20health%20disorder%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fadolescent-mental-health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20most%20common%20mental%20health%20disorders%20among%20teens%20are%2C%20unsurprisingly%2C%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fmyths-about-parenting-teens%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20a%20teenager%20is%20challenging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20face%20rapid%20(and%20often%20overwhelming)%20emotional%2C%20physical%2C%20social%2C%20and%20financial%20changes.%20These%20changes%20make%20them%20%26quot%3Bvulnerable%20to%20mental%20health%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20WHO.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccf81ee7-c81b-42be-9d5b-8c95c720e39f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20absences%20are%20excused%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20student%20uses%20a%20mental%20health%20day%20in%20Illinois%2C%20the%20absence%20is%20considered%20excused.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-your-boss-can-legally-do-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20doctor's%20note%20is%20needed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20win%20for%20parents%20like%20me.%20Going%20to%20the%20doctor%20takes%20time%20and%20money%2C%20which%20we%20do%20not%20always%20have.%20Furthermore%2C%20using%20a%20mental%20health%20day%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20student%20needs%20to%20attend%20a%20medical%20appointment.%20Rather%2C%20they%20may%20be%20spending%20the%20day%20resting%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283d500d3-8e71-49c1-8311-113d60742ecb%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20has%20bad%20days%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20the%20student%20has%20a%20mental%20health%20diagnosis%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20every%20human%20has%20bad%20days%20when%20burrowing%20under%20the%20comforter%20and%20watching%20a%20favorite%20TV%20show%20is%20far%20more%20appealing%20than%20heading%20to%20work%2C%20whether%20that%20work%20be%20a%20paid%20job%2C%20daily%20tasks%2C%20or%20going%20to%20school.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20believe%20that%20when%20states%20allow%20mental%20health%20days%20for%20kids%2C%20they%20are%20working%20toward%20chipping%20away%20at%20mental%20health%20stigmas.%20Our%20family%20has%20used%20excused%20mental%20health%20days%20for%20medical%20appointments%2C%20counseling%20appointments%2C%20and%20a%20day%20off%20to%20mentally%20and%20physically%20rest%20and%20recalibrate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be0a17a1-0b2f-4511-9409-1624e545e354%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20believe%20in%20perfect%20attendance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20need%20to%20send%20the%20message%20to%20all%20kids%2C%20especially%20our%20teens%2C%20that%20taking%20breaks%20is%20acceptable%20and%20healthy.%20The%20rise-and-grind%20pressure%20will%20eventually%20wear%20anyone%20down.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20read%20their%20body%20cues%20and%20prioritize%20resting%2C%20reflecting%2C%20and%20recharging.%20The%20saying%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20pour%20from%20an%20empty%20cup%26quot%3B%20remains%20an%20accurate%20mental%20picture%20for%20us%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22732e7d65-0921-4ff8-a4ec-18927f101e6d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMental%20health%20issues%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPush%20through%20and%20toughen%20up%20aren't%20messages%20I%20want%20to%20send%20our%20kids%20regardless%20of%20what%20they%20are%20going%20through.%20We%20need%20to%20believe%20our%20kids%20when%20they%20tell%20us%2C%20through%20their%20words%20or%20behaviors%2C%20that%20their%20mental%20health%20isn't%20stable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForcing%20our%20kids%20to%20be%20a%20warm%20body%20in%20a%20classroom%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20learning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20because%20my%20kids%20are%20physically%20present%20in%20their%20classroom%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20are%20mentally%20(including%20academically)%20present.%20I%20believe%20that%20giving%20my%20kids%20the%20opportunity%20to%20rest%20at%20home%2C%20attend%20therapy%2C%20or%20seek%20the%20evaluation%20and%20help%20of%20a%20psychiatrist%20is%20much%20more%20beneficial%20than%20them%20sitting%20absently%20at%20a%20desk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmental-health-school-days-unexcused-illinois-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741959841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0a17b69253ccddf97c987%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmental-health-school-days-unexcused-illinois-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20mom%20of%20teens%2C%20I%20appreciate%20that%20my%20kids%20can%20stay%20home%20if%20they%20are%20having%20a%20hard%20mental%20health%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rachel%20Garlinghouse)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmental-health-school-days-unexcused-illinois-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20European%20country%20said%20it%20might%20no%20longer%20be%20comfortable%20buying%20F-35s%20because%20of%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22f-35%20lightning%20ii%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F56e6d9fd91058428008b6241%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPortugal%20appears%20to%20be%20getting%20cold%20feet%20over%20the%20purchase%20of%20US-made%20F-35s.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPortugal%20is%20reconsidering%20the%20purchase%20of%20F-35s%20over%20changing%20US%20relations%20with%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPortugal%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20spend%20%246%20billion%20transitioning%20its%20air%20force%20to%20the%20jet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20its%20defense%20minister%20said%20Donald%20Trump's%20stance%20toward%20NATO%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPortugal%20says%20it's%20uneasy%20about%20replacing%20its%20older%20US-made%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20with%20F-35s%20over%20doubts%20about%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20behavior%20toward%20the%20US's%20allies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20future%20access%20to%20maintenance%20and%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Portuguese%20Defense%20Minister%20Nuno%20Melo%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.publico.pt%2F2025%2F03%2F13%2Fpolitica%2Fentrevista%2Fnuno-melo-afasta-compra-f35-eua-causa-trump-mundo-ja-mudou-2125727%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20newspaper%20P%C3%BAblico%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20geopolitical%20environment%20in%20our%20choices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20most%20recent%20US%20posture%20toward%20NATO%20%26quot%3Bmust%20make%20us%20think%20about%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebest%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelo%2C%20who%20also%20leads%20Portugal's%20CDS-People's%20Party%2C%20did%20not%20entirely%20rule%20out%20buying%20the%20planes%2C%20but%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20already%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Portugal%20does%20reverse%20course%2C%20it%20would%20represent%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20lucrative%20contract%20for%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20the%20jet's%20manufacturer%2C%20that%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20all%20but%20locked%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20April%2C%20Portugal's%20air%20force%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Gen.%20Jo%C3%A3o%20Cartaxo%20Alves%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dn.pt%2F2235481395%2Fgeneral-cartaxo-alves-tenho-militares-que-chegam-a-pagar-150-mil-euros-para-se-desvincularem%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20pilot%20training%20with%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20had%20already%20begun%20ahead%20of%20an%20anticipated%20%246%20billion%20transition%20to%20the%20F-35.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-mile-long-factory-where-f-35-stealth-fighters-made-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35%20Lightning%20II%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20advanced%20fighter%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22152a49bc-4bef-4e16-a367-2e385653deff%5C%22%3EA%20chill%20in%20the%20air%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMelo's%20statements%20came%20amid%20a%20distinct%20chilling%20of%20relations%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20particularly%20over%20military%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20sidelined%20European%20leaders%20from%20recent%20Russia-Ukraine%20peace%20negotiations%20and%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20Europe's%20financial%20contributions%20to%20Ukraine's%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelo%20said%20Portugal%20had%20always%20seen%20the%20US%20as%20a%20reliable%20ally%20but%20recent%20US%20changes%20in%20stance%20toward%20NATO%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20must%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20US%20could%20place%20limitations%20on%20the%20maintenance%20and%20supply%20of%20components%20for%20the%20F-35%3A%20%26quot%3BEverything%20that%20has%20to%20do%20with%20ensuring%20that%20aircraft%20will%20be%20operational%20and%20used%20in%20all%20types%20of%20scenarios.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortugal%20is%20facing%20snap%20elections%20after%20its%20government%20lost%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20this%20week%2C%20throwing%20further%20uncertainty%20over%20the%20country's%20long-term%20stance%20toward%20the%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20European%20countries%20have%20F-35s%20in%20their%20fleets%2C%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20has%20industrial%20partnerships%20in%20six%20European%20nations.%20The%20company%20has%20described%20the%20F-35%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BNATO%20standard%20fighter%20of%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorway%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fma.no%2Faktuelt-og-media%2F2025%2Fna-har-norge-mottatt-49-av-52-f-35%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20that%20it%20had%20taken%20delivery%20of%20three%20more%20F-35s%2C%20bringing%20its%20fleet%20of%20the%20aircraft%20to%2049.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Netherlands'%20defense%20minister%2C%20Ruben%20Brekelmans%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20F-35%20partner%20countries%20remained%20fully%20committed%20to%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20BI%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bvalues%20our%20strong%20partnership%20and%20history%20with%20the%20Portuguese%20Air%20Force%20and%20looks%20forward%20to%20continuing%20that%20partnership%20into%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20questions%20about%20foreign%20military%20sales%20of%20the%20F-35%20were%20best%20addressed%20by%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportugal-reconsider-f35-purchase-trump-us-lockheed-martin-ukraine-russia-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741959600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d40bd3b8b41a9673faa635%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportugal-reconsider-f35-pur