Director%20-%20for%20a%20perfectly%20legitimate%20reason%2C%20as%20advance%20payment%20for%20a%20new%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20Rs%201.95%20crore%20was%20duly%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20perfectly%20legitimate%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20seemed%20to%20come%20from%20the%20MD's%20WhatsApp%20account.%20His%20photo%20was%20in%20the%20display%20section%2C%20but%20it%20was%20actually%20a%20fraudster%20who%20conned%20the%20officer%20into%20transferring%20nearly%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20for%20the%20MD%20and%20his%20company%20(and%20the%20accounts%20officer)%2C%20the%20Telangana%20Cyber%20Security%20Bureau%20stopped%20this%20'high-value%20cyber%20fraud'%20and%20recovered%20the%20entire%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReceived%20earlier%20today%2C%20the%20transfer%20was%20completed%20at%201.02%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20that%20the%20real%20Managing%20Director%20received%20a%20bank%20notification%20and%2C%20understandably%20worried%2C%20immediately%20contacted%20his%20accounts%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20told%20about%20the%20'WhatsApp%20message'%2C%20the%20MD%20confirmed%20he%20made%20no%20such%20request%2C%20and%20the%20company%20promptly%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20the%20National%20Cybercrime%20Reporting%20Portal%2C%20or%20NCRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCRP%20then%20swung%20into%20action%2C%20first%20to%20confirm%20the%20transaction%20had%20occurred%20and%20then%20to%20track%20down%20the%20money.%20It%20was%20difficult%2C%20initially%2C%20because%20certain%20details%20were%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20working%20with%20the%20company%20and%20the%20MD%2C%20and%20the%20bank's%20nodal%20officers%2C%20the%20money%20was%20eventually%20located%20and%2C%20miraculously%2C%20the%20entire%20Rs%201.95%20crore%20was%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20the%20criminals%20had%20not%20yet%20withdrawn%20any%20of%20the%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20such%20instance%20of%20cybercrime.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20men%20and%20women%2C%20including%20private%20individuals%20and%20companies%2C%20have%20been%20duped%20out%20of%20hard-earned%20money%20by%20fake%20messages%20and%20calls%2C%20prompting%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20the%20government%20to%20be%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20for%20example%2C%20also%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20fraudsters%20stole%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20via%20certain%20mobile%20apps.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20that%20celebrities%20are%20spared.%20For%20example%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%20social%20media%20influencer%20Akanksha%20Thakral%20lost%20Rs%201.1%20lakh%20after%20responding%20to%20what%20she%20thought%20was%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20an%20Axis%20Bank%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%20the%20national%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%2C%20a%20unit%20within%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20identified%20and%20blocked%20nearly%2060%2C000%20WhatsApp%20accounts%20used%20for%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%209.94%20lakh%20complaints%20had%20been%20filed%20with%20the%20Citizen%20Financial%20Cyber%20Fraud%20Reporting%20and%20Management%20System%2C%20junior%20Home%20Minister%20Sanjay%20Bandi%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20these%20more%20than%20Rs%203%2C431%20crore%20had%20been%20saved%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20combat%20this%20problem%2C%20the%20I4C%20has%20a%20dedicated%20helpline%20-%201930%20-%20to%20help%20citizens%20who%20have%20been%20defrauded%20by%20a%20cybercriminal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Telangana%20authorities%20have%20also%20issued%20a%20list%20of%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20for%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20cautious%20of%20money%20transfer%20requests%20via%20WhatsApp%2C%20email%2C%20or%20phone%20calls%2C%20even%20if%20they%20appear%20to%20come%20from%20senior%20executives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAlways%20verify%20payment%20requests%20directly%20through%20formal%20channels%20before%20making%20transactions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20suspect%20fraud%20report%20it%20immediately%2C%20either%20via%20the%201930%20helpline%20or%20on%20www.cybercrime.gov.in%20to%20increase%20the%20chances%20of%20recovering%20your%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741955400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7emhd6j8_cyber-crime-generic_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhyderabad-company-cyber-fraud-rs-1-95-crore-boss-message-whatsapp-whatsapp-message-from-boss-how-hyderabad-firm-nearly-lost-rs-1-95-crore-7923420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Hyderabad%20company%20was%20nearly%20tricked%20-%20via%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20that%20seemed%20to%20come%20from%20the%20firm's%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20-%20of%20nearly%20Rs%202%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20India%E2%80%99s%20Cleanest%20Villages%3A%20What%20They%E2%80%99re%20Doing%20Differently%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20think%20of%20a%20clean%20and%20green%20place%2C%20what%20comes%20to%20mind%3F%20A%20futuristic%20city%20with%20high-tech%20waste%20management%3F%20Maybe%20a%20well-manicured%20park%20in%20an%20urban%20neighbourhood%3F%20Surprisingly%2C%20some%20of%20the%20cleanest%2C%20most%20sustainable%20places%20in%20India%20aren%E2%80%99t%20in%20big%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20they%E