20to%20pay%20our%20bills%20right%20now.%20It's%20a%20lot%20harder%20in%20a%20way%20because%20I'm%20%26quot%3Bstuck%26quot%3B%20in%20things%20like%20our%20house%2C%20with%20rising%20costs%20I%20can't%20control%2C%20like%20property%20taxes%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20look%20back%20on%20that%20time%2C%20it%20does%20help%20me%20now%20because%20I%20realize%20how%20much%20of%20my%20life%20has%20always%20felt%20like%20waiting%20for%20the%20other%20foot%20to%20drop.%20So%2C%20a%20big%20part%20of%20me%20is%20just%20inclined%20to%20roll%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20entering%20adulthood%20amid%20the%20recession%20scarred%20me%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20I%20should%20be%20fighting%20for%20more%20or%20expecting%20better.%20But%20truthfully%2C%20if%20I%20can%20figure%20it%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20win%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20where%20we%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-parent-during-the-recession-low-expectations-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741954742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d43360585f1dff88b228a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-parent-during-the-recession-low-expectations-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20gave%20birth%20in%202008%20a%20week%20after%20graduating%20college.%20My%20husband%20still%20had%20a%20year%20to%20go%2C%20so%20I%20worked%20nights%20while%20he%20took%20care%20of%20our%20baby.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chaunie%20Brusie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-parent-during-the-recession-low-expectations-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brigadier%20Faces%20Case%20After%20Colonel's%20Wife%20Alleges%20Sex%20Abuse%20In%20