harm%20US%20companies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20imposed%20tariffs%20that%20will%20impact%20vehicles%20and%20parts%20made%20around%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20said%20in%20the%20letter%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20US%20manufacturer%20and%20exporter%2C%20Tesla%20encourages%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Trade%20Representative%20(USTR)%20to%20consider%20the%20downstream%20impacts%20of%20certain%20proposed%20actions%20taken%20to%20address%20unfair%20trade%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20exporters%20are%20inherently%20exposed%20to%20disproportionate%20impacts%20when%20other%20countries%20respond%20to%20US%20trade%20actions.%20The%20assessment%20undertaken%20by%20USTR%20of%20potential%20actions%20to%20rectify%20unfair%20trade%20should%20also%20take%20into%20account%20exports%20from%20the%20United%20States%26quot%3B%2C%20Tesla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20past%20trade%20actions%20by%20the%20United%20States%20have%20resulted%20in%20immediate%20reactions%20by%20the%20targeted%20countries%2C%20including%20increased%20tariffs%20on%20electric%20vehicles%20imported%20into%20those%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%20where%20Musk%20is%20supporting%20a%20far-right%20political%20party%2C%20sales%20fell%20almost%2070%25%20compared%20to%20January%20last%20year.%20Per%20Time%20magazine%2C%20Tesla%20sold%207%2C517%20vehicles%20in%20Europe%20in%20January%2C%20half%20of%20what%20it%20sold%20in%20January%20the%20year%20prior.%20Tesla%20saw%20a%2050%25%20drop%20in%20sales%20in%20Portugal%20and%2045%25%20in%20France%20according%20to%20Reuters%2C%20while%20sales%20fell%2042%25%20in%20Sweden%20and%2048%25%20in%20Norway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20said%20on%20Truth%20Social%20this%20week%20%26quot%3BRadical%20Left%20Lunatics%2C%20as%20they%20often%20do%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20illegally%20and%20collusively%20boycott%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tues