is%2C%20it%20said%2C%20emerged%20after%20raids%20last%20week%20on%20the%20corporate%20offices%20of%20these%20distilleries%20and%20its%20employees%2C%20as%20also%20TASMAC%20and%20government%20offices%2C%20including%20those%20of%20%26quot%3Bkey%20associates%26quot%3B%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Balaji.%20These%20raids%20yielded%20%26quot%3Bincriminating%26quot%3B%20data%20about%20bar%20licence%20tenders%2C%20orders%20favouring%20some%20distilleries%2C%20and%20excess%20charges%20-%20Rs%2010%20to%20Rs%2030%20per%20bottle%20-%20at%20sales%20points%2C%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-reveals-rs-1-000-crore-irregularities-in-tasmac-7917967%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProbe%20Agency%20Reveals%20Rs%201%2C000%20Crore%20Irregularities%20In%20TASMAC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20also%20shows%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20claimed%2C%20that%20some%20distilleries%20%26quot%3Bsystematically%20inflated%26quot%3B%20expenses%20and%20%26quot%3Bfabricated%26quot%3B%20bogus%20purchases%20to%20siphon%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20in%20%26quot%3Bunaccounted%26quot%3B%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Balaji%20said%20the%20tenders%20had%20been%20executed%20online%20and%20that%20end-to-end%20procurements%20had%20been%20made%20for%2024%20districts.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20complete%20in%20the%20remaining%20districts%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProcurement%20(of%20alcohol%20from%20distilleries%20to%20stock%20TASMAC%20stores)%20was%20done%20based%20on%20an%20average%20of%20sales%20from%20the%20last%20three%20months.%20There%20was%20no%20concession%20to%20any%20distillery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20claims%20have%20triggered%20a%20political%20row%20in%20poll-bound%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20both%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly%20today%20during%20the%20budget%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Ftamil-nadu-budget-2025-bjp-aiadmk-walk-out-over-rupee-symbol-hindi-imposition-k-annamalai-eye-wash-bjp-slams-tamil-nadu-budget-its-4-mlas-and-aiadmk-w-7921828%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEye-Wash%26quot%3B%3A%20AIADMK%20Walks%20Out%20Of%20TN%20Budget%2C%20BJPs%204%20MLAs%20Follow%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20boss%20E%20Palaniswami%20later%20told%20reporters%20the%20alleged%20TASMAC%20scam%20could%20be%20worth%20as%20much%20as%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20demanded%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20and%20his%20government%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20didn't%20take%20any%20action%20even%20after%20the%20ED%20raid.%20We%20demand%20the%20DMK%20government%20should%20resign%20over%20this...%20ED%20has%20said%20there%20is%20corruption%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%20But%20it%20is%20possible%20there%20is%20actually%20corruption%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore.%20The%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20attacked%20the%20DMK%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20though%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20reserving%20its%20criticism%20for%20the%20'Hindi%20imposition'%20and%20the%20delimitation%20rows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20a%20sharp%20(but%20unspoken)%20jibe%20at%20the%20BJP's%20state%20unit%20chief%2C%C2%A0K%20Annamalai%2C%20Mr%20Balaji%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20someone%20shares%20information%20about%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20in%20an%20interview...%20you%20know%20who%20it%20is.%20Later%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20says%20the%20same%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%20I%20believe%20this%20means%20a%20thousand%20things%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Balaji%20also%20said%20his%20legal%20team%20would%20respond%20to%20questions%20about%20his%20surprise%2