C%20was%20ambushed%20by%20armed%20rebels.%20The%2030-hour%20siege%20ended%20in%20a%20deadly%20confrontation%20that%20left%2021%20civilians%20and%20four%20security%20personnel%20dead%2C%20while%20all%2033%20militants%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20final%20military%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20train%20driver%20Amjad%20recounted%20that%20the%20militants%20detonated%20an%20explosive%20under%20the%20train's%20engine%2C%20causing%20the%20bogies%20to%20derail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20the%20train%20stopped%2C%20Balochistan%20Liberation%20Army%20(BLA)%20terrorists%20launched%20an%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20terrorists%20breached%20the%20train%20by%20smashing%20windows%2C%20but%20they%20mistakenly%20believed%20we%20were%20dead.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20hundreds%20trapped%20inside%2C%20the%20ordeal%20was%20relentless.%20Survivors%20also%20said%20that%20the%20attackers%20separated%20passengers%20based%20on%20their%20region%20of%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescued%20passenger%20Arslan%20Yousaf%20recounted%20the%20militants'%20methodical%20violence.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20they%20took%20soldiers...%20and%20executed%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20referring%20to%20passengers%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20and%20security%20forces%20who%20were%20traveling%20on%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20times%2C%20they%20targeted%20specific%20individuals.%20If%20they%20had%20a%20grudge%20against%20someone%2C%20they%20shot%20him%20on%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreed%20hostage%20Mehboob%20Ahmed%2C%2031%2C%20suffered%20multiple%20gunshot%20wounds%20and%20described%20how%20some%20captives%20tried%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20two%20attempts.%20Some%20succeeded%2C%20but%20many%20were%20shot%20dead%20as%20the%20armed%20men%20opened%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20nearly%20lost%20hope%20for%20survival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20freed%20hostage%2C%20Muhammad%20Tanveer%2C%20said%20they%20were%20given%20only%20water%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalochistan%2C%20a%20resource-rich%20but%20insurgency-hit%20province%2C%20hosts%20major%20China-led%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20Gwadar%20Port%20and%20gold%20and%20copper%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Baloch%20rebels%20have%20long%20targeted%20security%20forces%2C%20installations%2C%20and%20foreign%20projects%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20recorded%20hijacking%20of%20a%20passenger%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20the%20Jaffar%20Express%20began%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20when%20BLA%20rebels%20blew%20up%20a%20section%20of%20railway%20track%2C%20forcing%20the%20train%20to%20stop%20in%20the%20rugged%20Bolan%20region%20of%20Balochistan.%20Armed%20with%20rocket%20launchers%2C%20automatic%20weapons%2C%20and%20grenades%2C%20the%20militants%20barged%20into%20the%20train.%20In%20the%20remote%20mountain%20pass%2C%20they%20took%20passengers%20hostage%20and%20engaged%20in%20a%20prolonged%20firefight%20with%20Pakistani%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Wednesday%2C%20Pakistan's%20military%20had%20launched%20a%20full-scale%20operation%20to%20retake%20the%20train.%20Pakistani%20military%20confirmed%20that%2021%20civilians%20died%20during%20the%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20security%20forces%20cleared%20the%20train%20bogey%20to%20bogey%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Pakistani%20army%20statement%20read.%20The%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%2C%20and%20Frontier%20Corps%20(FC)%20coordinated%20the%20counter-attack%2C%20with%20Pakistan's%20elite%20Special%20Services%20Group%20(SSG)%20commandos%20leading%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hours%20of%20intense%20fighting%2C%20all%2033%20militants%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20more%20than%20300%20passengers%20were%20successfully%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pakistan's%20military%20declared%20a%20complete%20victory%2C%20the%20BLA%20disputed%20the%20official%20account%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20still%20held%20hostages%20and%20that%20the%20battle%20was%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20spokesperson%2C%20Jeeyand%20Baloch%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20people%20Pakistan%20claimed%20to%20have%20rescued%20were%20actually%20released%20by%20the%20militants%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20the%20state%20has%20abandoned%20its%20hostages%20to%20die%2C%20it%20will%20also%20bear%20responsibility%20for%20their%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20traveled%20to%20Quetta%20on%20Thursday%20for%20a%20security%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741944780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjd1llb58_pakistan-trai-nhijack-reuters-_625x300_14_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-train-hijack-jaffar-express-crouched-for-hours-to-survive-pak-train-hijack-survivor-recalls-horror-7922370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20hostages%20crouched%20on%20the%20floor%20for%20as%20long%20as%2027%20hours%2C%20remaining%20motionless%2C%20while%20some%20could%20only%20gasp%20in%20shock%20as%20armed%20rebels%20entered%20the%20train%20and%20began%20executing%20passengers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-train-hijack-jaffar-express-crouched-for-hours-to-survive-pak-train-hijack-survivor-recalls-horror-7922370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chappell%20Roan%20accidentally%20joins%20Live%20battle%20with%20Punjabi%20man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741944566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2