%20replace%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20symbol%20with%20a%20new%20logo%20-%20Tamil%20alphabet%20'Ru'%20-%20has%20triggered%20a%20massive%20political%20controversy%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20language%20battle.%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20on%20Thursday%20released%20the%20logo%20online%20while%20unveiling%20the%20Budget%202025-26%20logo.%20This%20has%20drawn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromotes-secessionist-sentiments-n-sitharaman-slams-dmk-amid-rupee-row-7918163%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuge%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Opposition%2C%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bcondemnable%20and%20laughable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversial%20move%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20brought%20attention%20to%20an%20ironic%20fact%20-%20the%20now-dropped%20rupee%20symbol%20by%20the%20state%20was%20designed%20by%20a%20Tamilian%20man%2C%20D%20Udaya%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20D%20Udaya%20Kumar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frupee-symbol-designer-udaya-kumar-reacts-to-controversy-over-tamil-nadus-move-7920558%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ED%20Udaya%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20currently%20working%20as%20a%20professor%20at%20IIT%20Guwahati%2C%20designed%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20symbol%20in%202010%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20regime.%20He%20is%20the%20son%20of%20N%20Dharmalingam%2C%20a%20former%20DMK%20MLA%20who%20represented%20the%20Rishivandiyam%20constituency%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20design%20was%20chosen%20from%203%2C000%20entries%20submitted%20nationwide%2C%20and%20he%20received%20an%20award%20of%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%20The%20symbol%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20Indian%20and%20Roman%20letters%20-%20capital%20'R'%20and%20Devanagri%20'Ra'%20which%20represents%20rupaiah.%20It%20has%20two%20horizontal%20stripes%20at%20the%20top%2C%20symbolising%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bequal%20to%26quot%3B%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20officially%20adopted%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-dmk-ru-budget-language-war-national-education-policy-nep-designed-by-tamilian-k-annamalais-stupid-barb-at-dmk-amid-rupee-row-7915885%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rupee%20symbol%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2015%2C%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20website%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20a%20Bachelor's%20Degree%20in%20Architecture%20and%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20Design%20(visual%20communication).%20He%20completed%20his%20PhD%20in%20design%20from%20the%20Industrial%20Design%20Centre%2C%20IIT%20Bombay.%20The%20Indian%20rupee%20designer%20has%20also%20worked%20as%20a%20senior%20designer%20and%20then%20as%20a%20design%20head%20in%20a%20monthly%20magazine%20-%20Intelligent%20Computing%20CHIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20areas%20of%20interest%20include%20visual%20communication%20design%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20design%20research%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20Tamil%20typography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20he%20was%20proud%20of%20his%20creation%20but%20refused%20to%20snub%20the%20state%20government%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20decision%20did%20not%20impact%20him%20since%20a%20designer%20must%20be%20ready%20to%20face%20such%20challenges%20in%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20all%20our%20designs%20are%20successful%20or%20appreciated.%20You%20may%20also%20face%20criticism.%20As%20a%20designer%2C%20you%20always%20take%20them%20positively%2C%20learn%20from%20them%2C%20and%20move%20on.%20I%20do%20not%20see%20this%20(move)%20as%20disrespectful%20or%20a%20disregard%20of%20my%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741934040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fr0gn32v8_udaya-kumar_625x300_14_March_25.jpeg%22