ndefinite%20right%20to%20be%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vance%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20about%20'free%20speech.'%20Yes%2C%20it's%20about%20national%20security-but%20more%20importantly%2C%20it's%20about%20who%20we%2C%20as%20American%20citizens%2C%20decide%20gets%20to%20join%20our%20national%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVP%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40VP%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20A%20green%20card%20holder%20doesn't%20have%20an%20indefinite%20right%20to%20be%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20'free%20speech.'%20Yes%2C%20it's%20about%20national%20security%20%E2%80%94%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20it's%20about%20who%20we%2C%20as%20American%20citizens%2C%20decide%20gets%20to%20join%20our%20national%20community.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgRGn1subOy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgRGn1subOy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rapid%20Response%2047%20(%40RapidResponse47)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRapidResponse47%2Fstatus%2F1900338102725423342%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20law%20allows%20for%20the%20revocation%20of%20a%20green%20card%20under%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20including%20criminal%20activity%2C%20prolonged%20absence%20from%20the%20country%2C%20or%20failure%20to%20comply%20with%20immigration%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20'gold%20card'%20program%20would%20allow%20foreign%20nationals%20to%20purchase%20the%20right%20to%20live%20and%20work%20in%20the%20US%20for%20a%20%245%20million%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20selling%20a%20gold%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20said%20from%20the%20Oval%20Office%20recently.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20green%20car