i%20lies%20Theri%20Kaadu%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20red%20sand%20marvel%20spanning%20approximately%20500%20square%20kilometres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unique%20terrain%20is%20distinguished%20by%20its%20striking%20crimson%20dunes%2C%20shaped%20by%20time%20and%20the%20relentless%20forces%20of%20nature.%20The%20vibrant%20red%20hue%20of%20the%20sand%2C%20attributed%20to%20its%20high%20iron%20oxide%20content%2C%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F280183%2Findia-engineer-transforms-barren-rajasthan-thar-desert-into-forest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earid%20landscapes%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20how%20did%20this%20extraordinary%20desert%20come%20to%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20geological%20origins%20of%20Theri%20Kaadu%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheri%20Kaadu%E2%80%99s%20formation%20is%20a%20tale%20woven%20through%20millennia%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Quaternary%20Period.%20Literally%20translating%20to%20%E2%80%98red%20dune%20forest%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20desert%E2%80%99s%20origins%20lie%20in%20a%20complex%20interplay%20of%20marine%20deposits%20and%20aeolian%20(wind-driven)%20processes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Last%20Glacial%20Maximum%2C%20around%2010%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20sea%20levels%20were%20significantly%20lower%2C%20revealing%20an%20extensive%20sea%20shelf.%20%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20strong%20winds%20carried%20iron-rich%20sediments%20from%20this%20exposed%20shelf%20and%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20depositing%20them%20along%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20southeastern%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20